title: I promise I'm not crying

body: So I'm currently climbing the ranks on NA and EUW to do some fan games (Even with 300 ping), I'll let you guys know when I've got the alt's ready. I also wanted to know, Tonight games were more about me doing really well rather then the general humour, would you guys want to see more awesome/impressive plays, or would you want it to stay the way it is, Personally I don't want to change it, I'm happy with the current format, But I'm always looking for feedback.
